## Summary

- `ArtifactExporter` provides uniform access to scripts, DataFrames, and metadata
- `ArtifactConfig` controls storage mode: `memory`, `disk`, or `hybrid`
- `ArtifactDiff` computes overlap matrices and shared-feature counts
- `ArtifactDashboard` generates self-contained HTML reports
- `DataFrameStorage` abstracts away parquet/csv/feather backends
